snippet.title: The War Within Beta Trailer | World of Warcraft
snippet.description:
Xal’atath is taunting us as shadows gather deep within the heart of Azeroth. Band together to face the darkness. 

The World of Warcraft: The War Within Beta is Now Live! Be among the first to experience The War Within by pre-purchasing the Epic Edition to gain Beta access: https://shop.battle.net/product/world-of-warcraft-the-war-within

► Latest WoW news: http://worldofwarcraft.com/news 
► Subscribe to WoW: http://blizz.ly/WoWYTSub
